data.value:
MCNPX Tally Plotter was developed to easily plot data from MCTAL files created during MCNPX calculations.
This program requires that MCNPX is installed in order to work, including the component command line utility, MCPLOT. This program has been verified to work on Windows XP and Windows 7, with MCNPX 2.6.
